Class WebFingerConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wso2.carbon.identity.webfinger.WebFingerConstants

  • public class WebFingerConstants
extends Object
    This class contains all the rel types to be used in web finger. Any such constants should be added in future implementations.
